# Testing Agent Rules — TaskFlow AI

## Backend

- pytest-asyncio for async endpoints
- Target >80% coverage on `backend/`
- Health, auth, RBAC, and sanitization tests required per epic JSON

## Frontend

- Vitest + Testing Library
- Target >75% coverage on `frontend/`
- Validate forms with Zod schema tests

## Commands

```bash
uv run pytest --cov=backend --cov-fail-under=80
cd frontend && npm run test:coverage
```

